verbose_text: Stimulation of Dectin-1 with curdlan, a purified particulate beta-glucan, induced the robust production of TNF in wild-type BMDCs, whereas Vav1/2/3 deficient cells failed to produce TNF in response to Dectin-1 triggering (XREF_FIG F).
evidence: Dectin-1 with curdlan, a purified particulate beta-glucan              , induced the robust production of TNF
